data.title: China Country Code 86 Country Code CN
data.meta_description: EASY TO REMEMBER URL: 'CountryCode.org/china' for China country code 86 country codes CN and China phone number
data.text:
CountryCode.org is your complete guide to make a call from anywhere in the world, to anywhere in the world. This page details China phone code.

The China country code 86 will allow you to call China from another country. China telephone code 86 is dialed after the IDD. China international dialing 86 is followed by an area code.

The China area code table below shows the various city codes for China. China country codes are followed by these area codes. With the complete China dialing code, you can make your international call.
